<p>(panicked, panicked, panicking)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 恐慌：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When you are in a dangerous situation, <strong>don’t panic</strong>.
